## 5. Preview deployments for enhanced collaboration

Every deployment on Indobase Sites generates **preview links**, allowing developers and stakeholders to test changes before they go live. This improves collaboration and ensures thorough testing before final production deployment.

## 6. Multiple deployment options

Deploying a Vue application on Indobase Sites is flexible and straightforward:

- [Git-based deployments](/docs/products/sites/deploy-from-git): Automatically deploy changes when pushing to your repository.
